{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568970/extras/road_movie.gif?t=1710402631\" /><br><br>Torn Away is an interactive story about a girl torn away from home.<br><br>Cross all of Germany and Poland to get to the homeland and help Asya reunite with her family.<br><br>Along the way, you will find:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Levels in the spirit of classic adventure games</h2>Remember, life was peaceful once, and brighter days still await you in the future.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568970/extras/gif_3_600x300.gif?t=1710402631\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;Touching&quot; mini-games</h2>See the world through the eyes of a girl who was forced to grow up painfully quick.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568970/extras/gif_2_600x300.gif?t=1710402631\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Platformer with stealth mechanics</h2>Hide from soldiers and overcome obstacles in the harshest of weathers.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568970/extras/gif_4_600x300.gif?t=1710402631\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">First-person cinematic levels</h2>Put yourself in Asya's shoes and face the danger.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568970/extras/gif_1_600x300.gif?t=1710402631\" /><br><br>Will you be able to keep hope alive and return to your homeland?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Touching story inspired by the diaries of Soviet children about the hardships of wartime, told through the perspective of a little girl;<br></li><li>An unfairly forgotten theme of the fate of &quot;Ostarbeiters&quot; \u2014 people, who were forcibly deported from Eastern Europe to work in Nazi labor camps;<br></li><li>Visual language assembled from elements of socialist realism and modern French animation;<br></li><li>3D levels stylized as 2D art;<br></li><li>Original soundtrack inspired by the music of Hayao Miyazaki's movies, French New Wave cinema and experimental electronic music.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Torn Away","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/16c74a6f8d308b07e4ca702e2e067d770610c74c.jpg"},{"name":"Almost Alice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/dbad839842b9483f745d60130be7387b6acd60d3.jpg"},{"name":"Kind Soul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/fc0caeb9a49b45fd021dadef1960b27c81957763.jpg"},{"name":"War Is War","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/83be3e1b10bc7b5e5f85850b959c60c8ebf82cf5.jpg"},{"name":"Exemplary Student","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/2ce624f758c1a7eef7664e2cefb81e0161c1ae60.jpg"},{"name":"All by Herself","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/1770c72a9aad0f8c2ae9b20ad6e9b0c6585f84f0.jpg"},{"name":"Unexpected Guests","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/de65485b73de6c37093e2e7eb5fdaab11db5cf90.jpg"},{"name":"First Aid","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/9c6a163dece20b3078d28cc97475edefdf8bd03c.jpg"},{"name":"Daddy\u2019s Pride","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/381fe4ac8a94b87625bc42a3881968c30ec71568.jpg"},{"name":"Books Are Your Best Friend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1568970/933617787642b0a0401afebea3ed9a4b93d361d3.jpg"}],"total":35},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568970/page_b